moe.wyv.Sad_Bot

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • moe.wyv.Sad_Bot.Settings

  • public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all of the user-configurable settings to use in computations. It also allows for multiple bots to be written without having to rewrite code.

    fettuccine
